Visualizer website link - https://debt-settlement-visualizer.vercel.app/
💸 Debt Settlement Optimizer
Efficiently track, manage, and settle debts with our dynamic loan graph platform!
Visualize your debt network, minimize transactions, and discover the most influential users—all in one interactive website.

🚀 Project Overview
A smart platform to simplify group debts, minimize transactions, and visualize settlements.

🌟 Features
📊 Dynamic Debt Graph:
Real-time, directed loan graph to track who owes whom.

⚡ Greedy Settlement Algorithm:
Automatically computes the most efficient way to settle debts, minimizing both the number and total value of transactions.

🏅 Most Influential User:
Identifies the key user in your debt network using shortest path algorithms.

🔗 Minimized Debt Chains:
Simplifies complex debt cycles and optimizes settlement paths.

🌐 Interactive Visualization:
Explore and understand your debt network visually through an intuitive web interface.

